extracted_text:
H) TR Transitional District.
Purpose: This intent of this district is to serve as a transition between residential and more
intensive districts. This includes residential and commercial uses with a low noise and traffic
impact which would generally be considered compatible with a residential area which may or
may not have buffering requirements as documented in section 19 of this Ordinance. Uses in
this district which require potable water or sanitary sewer must be connected to municipal
water and municipal sewer.
llm_output.rationale: The text provides information about the TR (Transitional) district, but does not specify a maximum lot coverage value. The description focuses on the purpose and general characteristics of the district rather than specific dimensional requirements.
